defaultf)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThose who are ineligible for legal aid under the new provisions are likely to be the most vulnerable people in society, including families with children. Some of them may be 
defaultunable to leave the UK through no fault of their own, such as having an outstanding application with the Home Office; pregnancy; ill-health preventing air travel; or a lack of relevant documents;  
