defaultWe acted for F in 2 applications fdefaultor judicial review of a decision of the CPS not to prosecute her ex-partner with rape and sexual offences.default  F resides in Ireland with her 2 small children.  Both applications challenged the decisions of the CPS who had failed to protect F as a victim of se
